{"tid":829721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★【踼爆！】香港人做義工鋸樹 目的疑為私利","createTime":"2018-09-20T16:09:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T13:18:02.000Z","uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"075c1b21fbac483e425b6d3e7e3535a9c6e1cf6b","tid":829721,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:09:01.000Z","msg":"正當呢兩日大家都以為香港人守望相助之際，今日卻有打工仔在著名群組「大埔Group」出post引起激烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n話說有人發現咗原來一班「義工」鋸樹，<span style=\"color: red;\">原來有目的，就係鋸走樟樹，回家自用。眾所周知香樟木造價高</span>，唔知呢批「義工」會唔會鋸走再加工？又或者製作傢具？有區內居民回應，自言昨天亦見到類似情況，有班本土香港c9搬樹，更過份嘅係，明明樹都未死仍可以下泥，但已被「分屍」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%81%9A%E7%BE%A9%E5%B7%A5%E9%8B%B8%E6%A8%9F%E6%A8%B9-%E8%A2%AB%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E7%82%BA%E7%A7%81%E5%88%A9-032053640.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2581%259A%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E9%258B%25B8%25E6%25A8%259F%25E6%25A8%25B9-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%25A7%2581%25E5%2588%25A9-032053640.html&d=h7tbDmTK8csxJeeCU%2Bz0FcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=7b5c064d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%81%9A%E7%BE%A9%E5%B7%A5%E9%8B%B8%E6%A8%9F%E6%A8%B9-%E8%A2%AB%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E7%82%BA%E7%A7%81%E5%88%A9-032053640.html</a>"},{"pid":"8c7614379e46b8b452e5fe310fcda57343a7d478","tid":829721,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:09:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb01af0840397a4322e49061e12ea49199a9209e","tid":829721,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T1